      "text": "This is a **FirstGens Community** prototype - a clickable UX/UI prototype for a community platform built with React + TypeScript (no Frappe yet). It's schema-faithful to Frappe, mapping the prototype to three real Frappe apps:\n- `frappe/lms` - courses, lessons, quizzes\n- `frappe/gameplan` - teams, spaces, discussions, comments\n- `fg_companion` - custom app for events, mentor matching, AI settings\n\nWhat would you like to work on next? Options:\n1. Read the **Porting Guide** (schema mapping) to understand Frappe integration\n2. Check **Frappe Translation** files for UI text\n3. Look at the **Proprietary Algorithms** doc\n4. Explore the actual Frappe apps (`frappe/lms` and `frappe/gameplan`) for integration\n5. Work on the new `fg_companion` custom app\n\nWhat interests you most?",
